  "siteName": "谷歌开发者",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-backh=\"172\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100112958\" data-ratio=\"0.2972222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f0fcebf-9298-4185-ee28-355a1cc52c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f0fcebf-9298-4185-ee28-355a1cc52c00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p mpa-font-style=\"mb7m9nrx1r25\" style=\"font-size: 14px;text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.5em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mb7m9nsg1kof\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(147, 147, 147);font-style: italic;\">作者 / Gemini API 和 Google AI Studio 高级产品经理 Logan Kilpatrick</span></span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mb7m55p611yh\"><span leaf=\"\">我们目睹了开发者使用&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">Gemini 2.5 Pro</span>&nbsp;取得了令人赞叹的成就。因此，我们决定提前数周发布更新版本，以便开发者尽早体验新版模型。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 2.5 Pro</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\">https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/pro/</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: normal;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">我们很高兴宣布推出 Gemini 2.5 Pro 预览版 (I/O 版本)。此更新版本搭载更强大的编码能力，大幅提升了前端与界面开发能力；同时，其处理代码转换和编辑、复杂智能体工作流构建等基础编码任务的能力也有所提升。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"js_blockquote_wrap\" style=\"padding-top:4px;margin:1em 0;text-indent:0;border-left:3px solid #DBDBDB;padding-left:10px;font-size:15px;\">\n   <section class=\"js_blockquote_digest\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">我们发现，Gemini 2.5 Pro 是当前 \"能力与延迟\" 时间比率表现最出色的尖端模型。我很期待将此模型应用到 Replit Agent，尤其是在当我们面对对延迟敏感的任务时，需要更可靠的时效性。</span></span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section class=\"blockquote_info js_blockquote_source\" data-json=\"%7B%22type%22%3A%22out%22%2C%22article%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22from%22%3A%22Replit%20%E6%80%BB%E8%A3%81%20Michele%20Catasta%22%7D\">\n    <span class=\"blockquote_other\"><span leaf=\"\">Replit 总裁 Michele Catasta</span></span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <section style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <section style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;width: auto;height: auto;margin-left: 15px;border-left: 1px dotted rgb(70, 70, 70);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;line-height: 0;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: left;margin: 14px 0% -7px;transform: translate3d(-4px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 7px;width: 7px;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 3px 0px inset;\">\n         <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <section style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <section style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">一流的前端 Web 开发能力</span></strong></p>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 2.5 Pro 现居&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">WebDev Arena 排行榜首位</span>，该榜单主要对用户对于模型所构建 Web 应用的美观度与实用性的偏好进行排名。凭借自身的卓越能力，Gemini 2.5 Pro 为 Cursor 的创新代码智能体提供支持，并赋能我们与 Cognition 和 Replit 等公司之间的合作。我们正携手拓展智能体编程的边界，为开发者解锁新的可能。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/144e71f2-3ac6-4c46-de6d-b97639b79f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"100112957\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/144e71f2-3ac6-4c46-de6d-b97639b79f00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"js_blockquote_wrap\" style=\"padding-top:4px;margin:1em 0;text-indent:0;border-left:3px solid #DBDBDB;padding-left:10px;font-size:15px;\">\n   <section class=\"js_blockquote_digest\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">新版 Gemini 2.5 Pro 在我们的初级开发者评估中表现出众。这是有史以来第一个能完成对请求路由后端进行大规模代码重构的评估模型。该模型的表现宛如资深开发者，不仅能够做出正确的判断，还可选择恰当的抽象方案。</span></span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section class=\"blockquote_info js_blockquote_source\" data-json=\"%7B%22type%22%3A%22out%22%2C%22article%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22from%22%3A%22Cognition%20%E5%88%9B%E5%A7%8B%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%20Silas%20Alberti%22%7D\">\n    <span class=\"blockquote_other\"><span leaf=\"\">Cognition 创始团队成员 Silas Alberti</span></span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><br></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">WebDev Arena 排行榜首位</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\">https://web.lmarena.ai/leaderboard</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);overflow: hidden;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(83, 98, 242, 0);margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <section style=\"margin-right: 0%;margin-bottom: 3px;margin-left: 0%;text-align: justify;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;height: auto;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px 0px 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(127, 127, 127) rgb(70, 70, 70);background-color: rgba(84, 98, 242, 0);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 4px 0px inset;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;\">\n     <section style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;justify-content: flex-start;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;width: auto;height: auto;margin-left: 15px;border-left: 1px dotted rgb(70, 70, 70);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;line-height: 0;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: left;margin: 14px 0% -7px;transform: translate3d(-4px, 0px, 0px);\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 7px;width: 7px;border-width: 1px;border-radius: 10px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(70, 70, 70);box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 3px 0px inset;\">\n         <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: 88%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;\">\n       <section style=\"margin-top: 3px;margin-right: 0%;margin-left: 0%;transform: translate3d(-8px, 0px, 0px);text-align: left;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n        <section style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);text-align: justify;font-size: 20px;\">\n         <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 67, 53);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 2.5 Pro 的实际应用</span></strong></span></p>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\">凭借对代码的深刻理解和强大的推理能力，Gemini 2.5 Pro 持续成为开发者的首选模型。我们对该模型在以下案例中的应用尤为期待：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><br></span></p>\n  <section style=\"will-change: transform;margin-bottom: 0px;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n   <section style=\"display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;margin-top: 10px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;\">\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;align-self: center;margin-right: 4px;\">\n     <section style=\"transform: perspective(0px);transform-style: flat;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: center;transform: rotateX(180deg);\">\n       <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 20px;width: 3px;background-color: rgb(234, 67, 53);\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;align-self: center;\">\n     <section style=\"transform: perspective(0px);transform-style: flat;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: center;transform: rotateX(180deg);\">\n       <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 10px;width: 3px;background-color: rgb(234, 67, 53);\">\n        <svg viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" style=\"float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;\"></svg>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;border-bottom: 0px solid rgb(169, 207, 245);border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;flex: 0 0 auto;vertical-align: middle;align-self: center;width: auto;min-width: 5%;height: auto;padding-right: 12px;padding-left: 12px;\">\n     <section style=\"text-align: le f t;font-size: 15px;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">视频到代码</span></strong></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: auto;flex: 0 0 0%;height: auto;align-self: center;margin-right: 4px;\">\n     <section style=\"transform: perspective(0px);transform-style: flat;\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: center;transform: rotateX(180deg);\">\n       <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;height: 10px;width: 3px;background-color: rgb(234, 67, 53);\">\n 