xt-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\">https://console.cloud.google.com/freetrial?redirectPath=/vertex-ai/studio</span></span></p></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: normal;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于已经使用 Gemini 2.5 Pro 的开发者用户，新版本不仅能够提升编码性能，还将针对关键开发者反馈进行优化，包括降低函数调用错误率、提高函数调用触发率等。现有用户无需任何操作，即可自动升级到最新版本 (上一迭代 03-25 版本已指向 05-06 版本)，且<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">价格</span>保持不变。此外，我们还同步<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\">更新了 2.5 Pro 新版本的模型卡</span>。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><br></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">价格</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\">https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/pricing<a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mb7n4z4s-st5c71\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\">#gemini</a>-2.5-pro-preview</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(66, 133, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\">更新了 2.5 Pro 新版本的模型卡</span></span>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: left;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(147, 147, 147);\"><span leaf=\"\">https://modelcards.withgoogle.com/model-cards</span></span></p></li></ul>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
